The system implemented here is described in

  
  Hendrik Buschmeier, Timo Baumann, Benjamin Dorsch,
  Stefan Kopp and David Schlangen (2011).
  "Combining Incremental Language Generation and Incremental
  Speech Synthesis for Adaptive Information Presentation".
  in Proceedings of SIGDial, Seoul, Korea.

For your convenience, a bibtex entry for the paper is given below:

